            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h6>The Consultation</h6><p>Meet with our designers via a home visit in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}, or in our showroom to discuss your ideas, budget, and inspiration. We'll discuss your vision for gemstones, metals, and design preferences. We listen to your story.</p>",
