    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_Jg8nTk": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What kind of jewellery can I create through your bespoke design service?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We have the expertise to create a wide range of bespoke jewellery, including:</p><ul><li>Engagement rings and wedding bands</li><li>Necklaces and pendants</li><li>Bracelets and bangles</li><li>Earrings</li><li>Cufflinks and other men's jewellery</li><li>Heirloom recreations and adaptations</li></ul><p>Whether you have a clear idea or need inspiration, our team can design and craft virtually any piece of fine jewellery.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How long does the bespoke process take?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Typically, a bespoke commission takes between 4 to 8 weeks from the final design approval to the finished piece. This allows time for sourcing gemstones, casting, hallmarking, and setting.</p><p>The timeline for a bespoke jewellery commission can vary significantly depending on the complexity of the design, the materials chosen, and the level of detail involved. After the design is finalised and materials are selected, we will provide you with a more accurate estimated timeframe.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can I reuse gold or gemstones from old jewellery?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. <a href=\"/pages/jewellery-remodelling-service\" title=\"Jewellery Remodelling Service\">Remodelling </a>family heirlooms is one of our specialities. We can often melt down your yellow gold to create a new band, or reset your diamonds into a modern platinum setting.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do I need to book an appointment?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We invite you to experience our jewellery in the way that suits you best. You can book a private consultation to visit our showroom and view our collection in person.</p><p>We also offer <a href=\"/pages/home-visits\" title=\"Home Jewellery Viewing Chichester\">Home Visits</a> where you can arrange for an expert jeweller to bring our collection to your home in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. While we love welcoming clients to our workshop, we can also start the process via a video call.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Where is your Showroom located?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Our showroom is located at 64 South Street, Chichester, PO19 EE. You can find a map, parking information, and our full opening hours on our <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact Us\">Contact Us</a> page.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
